
# Chinese Learning App - Course API Tests

### 1. 健康检查
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### 2. 获取所有课程
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/courses

### 3. 按级别筛选课程 (L0)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/courses?level=L0

### 4. 获取课程详情 (第一个课程)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/courses/1

### 5. 获取课时详情
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lessons/1

### 6. 注册新用户
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "learner@test.com",
    "password": "123456",
    "nickname": "中文学习者"
}

### 7. 登录获取 Token
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "learner@test.com",
    "password": "123456"
}

### 7.1 登录默认管理员
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@chineseapp.com",
    "password": "Admin123456"
}

### 8. 获取学习进度 (需要普通用户 Token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/progress
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 9. 更新学习进度 (需要普通用户 Token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/progress/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "score": 85
}

### 10. 获取学习统计 (需要普通用户 Token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/stats
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 11. 新增课程 (需要管理员 Token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/courses
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "title": "L3 场景表达进阶",
    "description": "学习更复杂的中文场景表达",
    "level": "L3",
    "levelName": "中级",
    "thumbnail": "",
    "sortOrder": 4,
    "isPublished": true
}

### 12. 编辑课程 (需要管理员 Token)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/courses/4
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "title": "L3 场景表达进阶（更新版）",
    "description": "学习更复杂的中文场景表达与礼貌说法",
    "level": "L3",
    "levelName": "中级",
    "thumbnail": "",
    "sortOrder": 4,
    "isPublished": true
}

### 12.1 快捷切换课程发布状态 (需要管理员 Token)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/courses/4/publish
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "isPublished": false
}

### 12.2 批量重排课程顺序 (需要管理员 Token)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/courses/reorder
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "courseIds": [1, 2, 3, 4]
}

### 12.3 上传课程封面 (需要管理员 Token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/courses/4/upload
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=Boundary123

--Boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="course-cover.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< PASTE_LOCAL_IMAGE_FILE_HERE
--Boundary123--

### 12.4 删除课程封面 (需要管理员 Token)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/courses/4/thumbnail
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 13. 新增课时 (需要管理员 Token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/courses/4/lessons
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "title": "第1课：机场改签",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "content": "{\"introduction\":\"学习航班改签常用表达\",\"content\":\"我想改签到明天上午的航班。\"}",
    "audioUrl": "",
    "sortOrder": 1,
    "isFree": true,
    "xpReward": 30
}

### 14. 编辑课时 (需要管理员 Token)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lessons/11
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "courseId": 4,
    "title": "第1课：机场改签与值机",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "content": "{\"introduction\":\"学习机场改签与值机表达\",\"content\":\"我想改签到明天上午的航班，还想确认行李额度。\"}",
    "audioUrl": "",
    "sortOrder": 1,
    "isFree": true,
    "xpReward": 35
}

### 14.1 批量重排课时顺序 (需要管理员 Token)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/lessons/reorder
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "courseId": 4,
    "lessonIds": [11, 12, 13]
}

### 15. 删除课时 (需要管理员 Token)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lessons/11
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 16. 删除课程 (需要管理员 Token)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/courses/4
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
